parameters.name: BX
parameters.description:
JMXYZ X component of the magnetic-field component in nT.                
      X is in the plane containing Z and the IAU_JUPITER (S3 1997)            
      Prime Merdian.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description:
JMXYZ Y component of the magnetic field component in nT.                
      Y completes the right handed set (Z x X).

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description:
JMXYZ Z component of the magnetic field component in nT.                
      Z is the Jupiter dipole.
